    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 160245.0,
      "end_time": 165868.0,
      "text": "The early Muslim community was tribal, and so deeply entrenched in social status,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165868.0,
      "end_time": 170017.0,
      "text": "and the idea that a slave would look like a free woman,"
