    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172080.0,
      "end_time": 174309.0,
      "text": "And then there was the matter of practicality."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174309.0,
      "end_time": 176430.0,
      "text": "How would a slave do her work?"
