    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 215596.0,
      "end_time": 220775.0,
      "text": "A woman&#39;s way of dress should be based on custom and function."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220775.0,
      "end_time": 224615.0,
      "text": "So, what does that mean for a Muslim woman living in America today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
