    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 285749.0,
      "end_time": 292338.0,
      "text": "Maybe the requirement that a woman veil is in a different part of the Quran."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 292338.0,
      "end_time": 297509.0,
      "text": "For those of you who don&#39;t know, the Quran consists of 114 chapters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297509.0,
      "end_time": 302609.0,
      "text": "each chapter is written out in verses, like poetry."
