    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 324573.0,
      "end_time": 329611.0,
      "text": "because of their role, their function in society as his wives."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329611.0,
      "end_time": 331933.0,
      "text": "And the third verse is similar to the first,"
