    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 387206.0,
      "end_time": 392636.0,
      "text": "Turns out, God doesn&#39;t give a bullet point of all the parts on a woman&#39;s body"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 392636.0,
      "end_time": 394576.0,
      "text": "that he wants hidden from view."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 394576.0,
      "end_time": 399146.0,
      "text": "And in fact, it might be argued, and it is argued,"
