    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 414167.0,
      "end_time": 417857.0,
      "text": "according to her specific culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 417857.0,
      "end_time": 421928.0,
      "text": "and the progression of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 421928.0,
      "end_time": 424829.0,
      "text": "And that the term &quot;hijab,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 424829.0,
      "end_time": 426639.0,
      "text": "guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 426639.0,
      "end_time": 429796.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not in any of these three verses."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 429796.0,
      "end_time": 437059.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s nowhere in the Quran, directly meaning a woman&#39;s veil."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 437059.0,
      "end_time": 440149.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not to say that the word doesn&#39;t appear in the Quran"
