    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 455340.0,
      "end_time": 457948.0,
      "text": "or between believers and non-believers."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 457948.0,
      "end_time": 461098.0,
      "text": "Or it means a barrier, like a physical screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 461098.0,
      "end_time": 464621.0,
      "text": "that men during Muhammad&#39;s time were asked to stand behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 464621.0,
      "end_time": 466860.0,
      "text": "when speaking to his wives."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 466860.0,
      "end_time": 471470.0,
      "text": "Or it means the seclusion, the separation that Mary sought"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 471470.0,
      "end_time": 475010.0,
      "text": "when she was giving birth to Jesus."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 475010.0,
      "end_time": 477562.0,
      "text": "That separation and seclusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 477562.0,
      "end_time": 479393.0,
      "text": "that means hijab;"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 479393.0,
      "end_time": 481092.0,
      "text": "that physical screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 481092.0,
      "end_time": 482532.0,
      "text": "that means hijab;"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 482532.0,
      "end_time": 484757.0,
      "text": "that barrier, that divide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 484757.0,
      "end_time": 486577.0,
      "text": "that means hijab."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 486577.0,
      "end_time": 491954.0,
      "text": "Hijab doesn&#39;t mean a woman&#39;s veil."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 491954.0,
      "end_time": 496954.0,
      "text": "And yet, isn&#39;t it strange that what the term actually means,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 496954.0,
      "end_time": 502693.0,
      "text": "being screened off, divided away, barred, separated out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 502693.0,
      "end_time": 506164.0,
      "text": "these are the very terms that come to our minds"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 506164.0,
      "end_time": 509984.0,
      "text": "when we think of a Muslim woman?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 509984.0,
      "end_time": 511684.0,
      "text": "Why shouldn&#39;t they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 511684.0,
      "end_time": 516025.0,
      "text": "We have all seen the way some Muslim women are treated around the world:"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 516025.0,
      "end_time": 518034.0,
      "text": "if she attempts to go to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 518034.0,
      "end_time": 519952.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s shot in the head;"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 519952.0,
      "end_time": 521794.0,
      "text": "if she attempts to drive a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 521794.0,
      "end_time": 523208.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s jailed;"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 523207.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524814.0,
      "text": "if she attempts to take part"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 524814.0,
      "end_time": 527885.0,
      "text": "in the political uprisings happening in her own country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 527885.0,
      "end_time": 529935.0,
      "text": "to be heard, to be counted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 529935.0,
      "end_time": 531945.0,
      "text": "she is publicly assaulted."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 531945.0,
      "end_time": 535505.0,
      "text": "Forget about hiding out in the dark at the outskirts of the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 535505.0,
      "end_time": 540093.0,
      "text": "some men now feel comfortable enough to assault a woman on the sidewalk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 540093.0,
      "end_time": 543075.0,
      "text": "for the world to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 543075.0,
      "end_time": 546656.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t care to hide their identities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 546656.0,
      "end_time": 550285.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re more interested in making international headlines."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 550285.0,
      "end_time": 554105.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re too busy making videos and uploading them onto YouTube,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 554105.0,
      "end_time": 556675.0,
      "text": "bragging about what they&#39;ve done."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 556675.0,
      "end_time": 560885.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t they care to hide their crimes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 560885.0,
      "end_time": 563885.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t feel like they&#39;ve committed any crimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 563885.0,
      "end_time": 566585.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the women who&#39;ve committed the crimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 566585.0,
      "end_time": 570015.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the women who got these funny ideas in their heads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 570015.0,
      "end_time": 572235.0,
      "text": "ideas that actually led them out of the house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 572235.0,
      "end_time": 573522.0,
      "text": "led them into society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 573522.0,
      "end_time": 576485.0,
      "text": "believing that they can make a contribution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 576485.0,
      "end_time": 578209.0,
      "text": "and we all know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 578209.0,
      "end_time": 581226.0,
      "text": "honorable women, they stay at home;"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 581226.0,
      "end_time": 583776.0,
      "text": "honorable women stay invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 583776.0,
      "end_time": 588205.0,
      "text": "Just as it was the custom for honorable women to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 588205.0,
      "end_time": 592845.0,
      "text": "during the Prophet&#39;s time."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 592845.0,
      "end_time": 595366.0,
      "text": "Is that true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 595366.0,
      "end_time": 600438.0,
      "text": "1400 years ago is long before feminism."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 600438.0,
      "end_time": 607118.0,
      "text": "Were women locked away behind doors, screened off by veils?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 607118.0,
      "end_time": 610288.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out that the Prophet&#39;s first wife"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 610288.0,
      "end_time": 613128.0,
      "text": "was what we would define today"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 613128.0,
      "end_time": 615348.0,
      "text": "as a CEO."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 615348.0,
      "end_time": 617418.0,
      "text": "She was a successful merchant"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 617418.0,
      "end_time": 623049.0,
      "text": "whose caravan equaled the caravans of all the other traders put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 623049.0,
      "end_time": 628219.0,
      "text": "She essentially headed up a successful import-export company."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 628219.0,
      "end_time": 633019.0,
      "text": "When she hired Muhammed to work for her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 633019.0,
      "end_time": 636890.0,
      "text": "she was so taken with his honesty"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 636890.0,
      "end_time": 639859.0,
      "text": "that eventually she proposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 639859.0,
      "end_time": 641489.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 641489.0,
      "end_time": 643769.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not sure how many women feel comfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 643769.0,
      "end_time": 647030.0,
      "text": "proposing marriage to a man today."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 647030.0,
      "end_time": 649960.0,
      "text": "And Muhammad&#39;s second wife?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 649960.0,
      "end_time": 652440.0,
      "text": "She was no slacker either."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 652440.0,
      "end_time": 654920.0,
      "text": "She rode into battle on the back of a camel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 654920.0,
      "end_time": 658529.0,
      "text": "which is equivalent to a woman riding into battle today"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 658529.0,
      "end_time": 662570.0,
      "text": "inside of a Humvee or a tank."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 662570.0,
      "end_time": 665440.0,
      "text": "And what of the other women?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 665440.0,
      "end_time": 669369.0,
      "text": "Early records show that women demanded to be included"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 669369.0,
      "end_time": 673281.0,
      "text": "in the Islamic revolution taking place around the Prophet."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 673281.0,
      "end_time": 676270.0,
      "text": "One woman became famous as a general"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 676270.0,
      "end_time": 682410.0,
      "text": "when she led her army of men into battle and crushed a rebellion."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 682410.0,
      "end_time": 687231.0,
      "text": "Men and women freely associated with one another, exchanged gifts."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 687231.0,
      "end_time": 694160.0,
      "text": "It was custom for a woman to select her own husband and propose."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 694160.0,
      "end_time": 696650.0,
      "text": "And when things didn&#39;t work out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 696650.0,
      "end_time": 699081.0,
      "text": "to initiate divorce."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 699081.0,
      "end_time": 705581.0,
      "text": "Women even loudly debated with the Prophet himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 705581.0,
      "end_time": 707930.0,
      "text": "Seems to me that if fundamentalists"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 707930.0,
      "end_time": 713271.0,
      "text": "want to return current Muslim society to 680 AD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 713271.0,
      "end_time": 716611.0,
      "text": "it might be a huge step forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 716611.0,
      "end_time": 718251.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 718251.0,
      "end_time": 720201.0,
      "text": "Progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 720201.0,
      "end_time": 726023.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 726023.0,
      "end_time": 729540.0,
      "text": "But we still have to answer an important question."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 729540.0,
      "end_time": 735500.0,
      "text": "If not from Islamic history, and if not from the Quran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 735500.0,
      "end_time": 738012.0,
      "text": "how is it that we, in the modern era,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 738012.0,
      "end_time": 742599.0,
      "text": "have come to associate Muslim women with hijab?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 742599.0,
      "end_time": 746511.0,
      "text": "With being separated out from society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 746511.0,
      "end_time": 748642.0,
      "text": "secluded and isolated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 748642.0,
      "end_time": 754438.0,
      "text": "barred from the most basic human rights?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 754438.0,
      "end_time": 759570.0,
      "text": "I hope it&#39;s not any surprise to you that this isn&#39;t by accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 759570.0,
      "end_time": 766522.0,
      "text": "For the past few decades, the very people who have been given the important task"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 766522.0,
      "end_time": 768962.0,
      "text": "of reading and interpreting the Quran"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 768962.0,
      "end_time": 772793.0,
      "text": "in a variety of different Muslim communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 772793.0,
      "end_time": 777093.0,
      "text": "certain clerics have been inserting a certain meaning"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 777093.0,
      "end_time": 780854.0,
      "text": "into those three verses concerning women."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 780854.0,
      "end_time": 785174.0,
      "text": "For instance that verse I told you about earlier:"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 785174.0,
      "end_time": 788264.0,
      "text": "&quot;O Prophet, tell your wives, your daughters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 788264.0,
      "end_time": 792746.0,
      "text": "and the women of the believers to draw upon themselves their garments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 792746.0,
      "end_time": 798744.0,
      "text": "this is better, so that they not be known and molested.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 798744.0,
      "end_time": 802494.0,
      "text": "Some clerics, not all, some clerics"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 802494.0,
      "end_time": 805795.0,
      "text": "have added a few words to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 805795.0,
      "end_time": 808235.0,
      "text": "so that in certain translations of the Quran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 808235.0,
      "end_time": 811245.0,
      "text": "that verse reads like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 811245.0,
      "end_time": 814855.0,
      "text": "&quot;O Prophet, tell your wives, your daughters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 814855.0,
      "end_time": 819353.0,
      "text": "and the women of the believers, to draw upon themselves their garments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 819353.0,
      "end_time": 823606.0,
      "text": "parentheses, a garment is a veil"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 823606.0,
      "end_time": 826146.0,
      "text": "that covers the entire head and the face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 826146.0,
      "end_time": 829085.0,
      "text": "the neck and the breast all the way down to the ankles"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 829085.0,
      "end_time": 831380.0,
      "text": "and all the way to the wrists."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 831380.0,
      "end_time": 836416.0,
      "text": "Everything on a woman&#39;s body is covered except for one eye"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 836416.0,
      "end_time": 839235.0,
      "text": "because she must see where she is headed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 839235.0,
      "end_time": 843046.0,
      "text": "and the hands must be covered in gloves."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 843046.0,
      "end_time": 844057.0,
      "text": "Because, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 844057.0,
      "end_time": 848077.0,
      "text": "there was certainly a lot of gloves back in the desert of Saudi Arabia."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 848077.0,
      "end_time": 849666.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 849666.0,
      "end_time": 853006.0,
      "text": "Etc., etc., etc., etc., on, and on, and on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 853006.0,
      "end_time": 854296.0,
      "text": "end of parentheses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 854296.0,
      "end_time": 860227.0,
      "text": "so that she not be known and molested.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 860227.0,
      "end_time": 863628.0,
      "text": "And what these so-called clerics"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 863628.0,
      "end_time": 868798.0,
      "text": "have concluded based on these types of insertions"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 868798.0,
      "end_time": 874788.0,
      "text": "is that a woman only has one function."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 874788.0,
      "end_time": 876809.0,
      "text": "To understand what that function is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 876809.0,
      "end_time": 881669.0,
      "text": "all you have to do is read some of the fatwas or legal rulings"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 881669.0,
      "end_time": 887080.0,
      "text": "that these so-called clerics have actually gone ahead and issued."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 887080.0,
      "end_time": 891059.0,
      "text": "Let me give you a sampling."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 891059.0,
      "end_time": 895050.0,
      "text": "A woman need only finish elementary school"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 895050.0,
      "end_time": 897640.0,
      "text": "before she gets married."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 897640.0,
      "end_time": 904409.0,
      "text": "Which puts her, what, at the ripe old age of 11, 12 years old?"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 904409.0,
      "end_time": 910270.0,
      "text": "A woman cannot fulfill her spiritual obligations to God"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 910270.0,
      "end_time": 916061.0,
      "text": "until she first fulfills her physical obligations to her husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 916061.0,
      "end_time": 921250.0,
      "text": "If he desires her while she sits on the mount of a camel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 921250.0,
      "end_time": 925181.0,
      "text": "she should submit."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 925181.0,
      "end_time": 931191.0,
      "text": "Islam has forbidden a woman from wearing a bra"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 931191.0,
      "end_time": 936232.0,
      "text": "because bras lift up and make a woman appear younger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 936232.0,
      "end_time": 941943.0,
      "text": "and this is calculated deception."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 941943.0,
      "end_time": 944773.0,
      "text": "My personal favorite:"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 944773.0,
      "end_time": 949464.0,
      "text": "if a man has an ulcer excreting puss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 949464.0,
      "end_time": 953502.0,
      "text": "from the top of his head to the bottom of his feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 953502.0,
      "end_time": 955863.0,
      "text": "and she licked it for him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 955863.0,
      "end_time": 962111.0,
      "text": "she would still not fulfill what she owes him."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 962111.0,
      "end_time": 968864.0,
      "text": "What these and the many other rulings just like it concerning women boil down to"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 968864.0,
      "end_time": 971044.0,
      "text": "is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 971044.0,
      "end_time": 976684.0,
      "text": "The best of women, the most honorable among them"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 976684.0,
      "end_time": 978754.0,
      "text": "is uneducated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 978754.0,
      "end_time": 981164.0,
      "text": "and so powerless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 981164.0,
      "end_time": 983964.0,
      "text": "not very different from a slave."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 983964.0,
      "end_time": 988524.0,
      "text": "So, she remains at home without complaint, without a bra."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 988524.0,
      "end_time": 989614.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 989614.0,
      "end_time": 997184.0,
      "text": "Ready and available at all times to satisfy his every whim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 997184.0,
      "end_time": 1001795.0,
      "text": "even if it&#39;s to lick his entire body;"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1001790.0,
      "end_time": 1004169.0,
      "text": "satisfying him whenever he calls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1004170.0,
      "end_time": 1011650.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s in his bed or on the mount of a camel."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1011650.0,
      "end_time": 1015845.0,
      "text": "Does this sound like God&#39;s will to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1015850.0,
      "end_time": 1019776.0,
      "text": "Does this sound like scripture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1019780.0,
      "end_time": 1025850.0,
      "text": "Or does this sound strangely, uncomfortably erotic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1025839.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1031231.9999999999,
      "text": "like the worst kind of misogynist fantasy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1031240.0,
      "end_time": 1033791.0,
      "text": "Are these so-called clerics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1033790.0,
      "end_time": 1036749.0,
      "text": "and the fundamentalists and extremists who support them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1036750.0,
      "end_time": 1040902.0,
      "text": "truly purifying Islam from within,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1040900.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1045619.0000000001,
      "text": "bringing it back to its intended form?"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1045619.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1049969.0,
      "text": "Or are these men no different from those men"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1049970.0,
      "end_time": 1054423.0,
      "text": "standing out in the dark at the outskirts of the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1054420.0,
      "end_time": 1059487.0,
      "text": "eager to prey upon a woman?"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1059490.0,
      "end_time": 1060891.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1060890.0,
      "end_time": 1070890.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}